              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "1. Experimental data sets were renormalized for decay",
                "    data and monitor reaction cross-section data to",
                "    obtain experimental data sig-exp(Ei).",
                "2. Model calculation was performed for three models",
                "    (EMPIRE, STAPRE, TALYS) to obtain model data",
                "    sig-mod(Ei).",
                "3. Polynomial fit was performed to the ratio",
                "    sig-exp(Ei)/sig-mod(Ei) to obtain smooth curve of",
                "    the normalization factor f(E).",
                "   The polynomial fit was performed twice.",
                "    Experimental data out of 3 times of the",
                "    uncertainty in f(E) were excluded, and then the",
                "    polynomial fit was performed again.",
                "4. Average of f(E)*sig-mod(E) from models was adopted",
                "    as the recommended cross section."
              ]
            }
          ],
